<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../cs/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/blog.css">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Mate+SC&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.7.2/animate.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
</head>

<body>


    <div class="blog-header">
        {{>navbar}}
        <div class="blog-header-text">
            <h1 class="blog">Blog</h1>
        </div>
    </div>


    <!-- ******* Loading effect******** -->
    <div class="loader">
        <div class="center">
            <div class="one"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{!-- ***************dark/light theme************ --}}
    <div class="theme">
        <input type="checkbox" class="checkbox" id="checkbox">
        <label for="checkbox" class="label">
            <img class="moon" src="img/moon.png" alt="">
            <img class="sun" src="img/sun.png" alt="">
            <div class="ball"></div>
        </label>
    </div>



    {{!-- ***************************Recent blog section******************** --}}
    <section class="col-md-12 mt-5">
        <div class="container p-0">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 article">
                    <h6 class="title pt-5">Recent Blog</h6>
                    <h4 class="title">Mohamaya Lake : How to visit, costing & travel guide.</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">26/07/2021</p>
                    <div class="article-img">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="feature-img">
                                <img src="img/mohamaya.jpg" class="big-img">
                            </div>
                            <div class="thumbnail">
                                <div class="small-img">
                                    <a href="img/mohamaya.jpg"><img src="img/mohamaya.jpg"></a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="small-img">
                                    <a href="img/mohamaya1.jpg"><img src="img/mohamaya1.jpg"></a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="small-img">
                                    <a href="img/mohamaya2.jpg"><img src="img/mohamaya2.jpg"></a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="small-img">
                                    <a href="img/mohamaya3.jpg"><img src="img/mohamaya3.jpg"></a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p>Brief Description of Mohamaya Lake: <br>
                        Mohamaya Lake is located in Mirshorai upazila of Chittagong (Chattogram) city. The natural
                        mountain lake Mohamaya is as beautiful as picture. Some travelers compare beauty of this lake
                        with Nepalâ€™s Pokhara & Hoping Island of Lankawi, Malaysia. This could be major attraction for
                        tourist if we highlight this lake to the travelers. Mohamaya lake is a paradise for birds, a
                        sanctuary for them. You can see the fishing technique of kingfisher here along with the diving
                        in the water of little cormorant bird. Even you can see variety of different birds species
                        during boating inside Mohamaya Lake. Birds will be very nearby you (within yards) during the
                        boating. From here you can enjoy waterfall also. It will take only 10-15 minutes journey to
                        reach the waterfall in speed boat. Hope this will place will help you to spent quality time with
                        your family and friends.
                        <br><br>
                        How to Travel to Mohamaya Lake: <br>
                        Mohamaya lake is located on the way to Chittagong from Dhaka. You have to get down from bus on
                        Mirshorai stoppage/Bus stand . From this part of main high way you have to move for 2-3
                        kilometer towards Mirshorai to reach Mohamaya Lake. It will take 15 minutes only to reach
                        Mohamaya lake from Mirshorai highway stoppage.
                        <br><br>
                        Costing: <br>
                        Dhaka to Chittagong Bus fare: 480 (Non AC), 1250 (AC)
                        Mirshorai stoppage/ Bus stand to Mohamaya Lake: Depends on negotiation.
                        Speed boat fare in Mohamaya Lake: 700 BDT per speed boat (capacity: 4 People)
                    </p>
                    <div class="ftr">
                        <div class="author">
                            <a href="#"> <img src="http://adamthemes.com/demo/code/cards/images/avatar3.png" alt=""
                                    class="avatar"> <span>Debbon Amet</span> </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stats"> <i class="fa fa-heart"></i> 365</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 mt-4">
                    <div class="container otherb">
                        <h4 class="title mt-5">Read More Blogs</h4>
                        <div class="row">
                            {{# each blogList}}
                            <div class="card">
                                <div class="card-image">
                                    <a href="#"> <img src="img/{{this.image}}"></a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="table">
                                    {{!-- <h6 class="date">{{{this.date}}}</h6> --}}
                                    <p class="card-description">{{this.title}}</p>
                                    <div class="ftr">
                                        <div class="author">
                                            <a href="#"> <img
                                                    src="http://adamthemes.com/demo/code/cards/images/avatar3.png"
                                                    alt="" class="avatar"> <span>{{this.name}}</span> </a>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="stats"> <i class="fa fa-heart"></i> 301</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            {{/each}}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>






    {{!-- **********************Post blog form**************** --}}

    <div class="container mt-5" id="create-blog">
        <div class="newblog">
            <div class="card-heading">
                <h2 class="titleB">Post new article</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="blog-form">
                <form action="/blog" method="POST">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="name">Full name</div>
                        <div class="value">
                            <input class="input" type="text" name="name" required="" placeholder="Enter your fullname">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="name">Title</div>
                        <div class="value">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <input class="input" type="text" name="title" placeholder="Title">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="name">Article</div>
                        <div class="value">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <textarea class="textarea" name="article"
                                    placeholder="Write your article here"></textarea>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="name">Upload Image</div>
                        <div class="value">
                            <div class="input-group js-input-file">
                                <input class="input-file" type="file" name="image" id="file">
                                <label class="label--file" for="file">Choose file</label>
                                <span class="input-file__info">No file chosen</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="label--desc">Upload relevant images. Max file size 50 MB</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a href="#" class="btn sub">Cancel</a>
                        <button class="btn sub" type="submit">Publish Post</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>




    {{!-- ************************************* --}}
    {{>footer}}

    <script src="../jq/jquery.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="../js/bootstrap.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
    <script>
        jQuery(document).ready(function ($) {
            "use strict"
            $('.thumbnail a').click(function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                $('.feature-img img').attr("src", $(this).attr("href"))
            })
        })

        const check = document.getElementById('checkbox')
        check.addEventListener('change', () => {
            document.body.classList.toggle('light')
        })

    </script>
</body>

</html>